Vege Link is an interesting, colourful, cute and classic puzzle game. The game can be very challenging to practice your reaction speed. 

Download Vege Link for FREE and link your way through different vegetables to unlock more fantastic levels. Have fun!

Vege Link features:
•	Start with 128 levels of Vege Link puzzles;
•	New target scores for each level;
•	Test your reaction speed;
•	Share the game with your friend;
•	Easy and fun to play;
•	Lovely UI and colourful.

How to play:
•	Tap with your finger and link to the same vegetables;
•	Link at least three vegetables of the same to score;
•	Achieve the target score for each level in the given time;
•	Many levels for your brain practice and challenge.

Play the game and enjoy the lovely vegetables. Our big THANK YOU goes out to everyone who has downloaded and played Vege Link!


